{"tid":995001,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] 大視后待遇與別不同 一場戲安排兩個替身上場","createTime":"2019-01-25T06:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T15:00:38.000Z","uid":82917,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1ddf60e2b3cebc2567d1085b73e1edf67a5b13fa","tid":995001,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">過氣造馬大視后</span> 唐詩詠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（37）</span></span>近年愛情事業兩得意，17年憑劇集《不懂撒嬌的女人》榮升視后後工作接踵而來，今年有《白色強人》同《調解師》兩套劇都擔正做女主角。愛情方面，佢亦成功收兵兩位身家過億嘅富家公子作契哥哥，包括姚子羚舊愛鄭子邦及升學顧問中心執行董事陳思銘。<br />\n<br />\n近日唐詩詠拍攝《調解師》去到西貢碼頭拍攝外景，睇得出佢嘅造馬大視后待遇與別不同，竟然有兩個替身，一場跳海戲有替身幫佢都算正常，但另一場行行企企嘅戲都有替身幫佢，睇得出導演對佢寵愛有加。<br />\n<br />\n不過唐詩詠都好識做，替身幫佢跳完海，佢都立即上前為濕透身嘅替身遞上熱飲保暖，又幫佢抹乾衣服，唔博上報幫替身抹黎把撚呀？難怪劇組都咁錫佢啦，快撚啲捧紅佢添呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59WvDAL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59WvDAL.png&h=f9443dd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"744e940b5cb5701b5baa71baca2e9680e8926a95","tid":995001,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13de12b8e3db2d73ade44f1af1386f0aefd82f3","tid":995001,"uid":183383,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:20:57.000Z","msg":"(37)"},{"pid":"54129c93d06dde3ff4f616e9d4ec134d7dcc2b7b","tid":995001,"uid":25857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:21:27.000Z","msg":"西"},{"pid":"3e57bc30e55a25ba3b82af45f9257ad037edb090","tid":995001,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3eb1fc3a3b2eee805c716c066e34dbb705c6e00","tid":995001,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"744e940b5cb5701b5baa71baca2e9680e8926a95","tid":995001,"uid":27064,